node.text: #TBT for real ⏪⏪⏪ This was my first single and first video EVER…. I wrote this song when I was 16 and couldn’t believe when it was released three years later. I was so nervous that I didn’t sleep for a week before shooting. Will always remember my first!! More videos coming on @enriqueiglesias https://www.youtube.com/enriqueiglesias
